cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.RO

The paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence (AI) agents that learn to perform tasks from sensory input, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which is a common technique in both machine learning and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of 3D virtual reality environments suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV), and the mention of solving tasks without strong simplifying assumptions suggests a focus on robotics (cs.RO).
